BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Q7rCUnjmVAlVu6ZyR53uH
SUMMARY:Tour De Pints
DTSTAMP:20260326T230624Z
DTSTART:20250517T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Tour de Pints is an annual bike ride throughout Seattle to 
	visit a bunch of breweries and drink a bunch of beer! Can't beat that!The 
	full route has not been announced yet\, but you can expect somewhere aroun
	d 25 miles of bike path\, bike lane\, and safe road riding that will take 
	you to approximately five breweries. The route will end in Ballard\, not t
	oo far from the start point. The ride is unsupported\, but there will be p
	lenty of food options around to keep you fueled up along the way.At each s
	top\, there will be raffles for prizes\, as if you need an excuse to ride 
	bikes and drink beers!The event is totally free to attend\, though donatio
	ns are accepted by purchasing a donation ticket. No purchase required. Dri
	nking beer is not required\, or even advisable. Know your limits!The route
	 will be revealed as the event draws nearer!RSVP Here: https://www.eventbr
	ite.com/e/tour-de-pints-2025-tickets-1317605195609\n\nFrom Seattle Beer We
	ek
